                <h1 class="p1">You've Taken That Step</h1>
                <p class="card-1">
                We raise intelligence and cure the feat of self-awareness existent in
                every discussion a human has had the privilege to engage in. Every
                facet of intelligence is confined in what you do for people, many of
                us fight half of the battle, and fail to recognize emotional
                intelligence. The abandonment of positive emotions leaves more room
                for dysfunction, and we must train ourselves to communicate in a way
                that leads to the mutual enhancement of intelligence.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
