      <div class="hero-container-2">
          <div class="info">
          <h1 class="p2">Media Repurposed</h1>
          <p class="card-2">
            Social Media is a marketplace where currency is social
            validation. It's hard to admit that we need the validation of others, 
            so conversation devolves into taking an eye for an eye, and meaningful
            discussion turns into an emotional turmoil of vengeance rather than
            the entertainment that can actually be found within the genuine
            vigilance of having an opposing view.
          </p>
      </div>
  </div>
