        <div class="info">
        <h1 class="p3">So... Why?</h1>
        <p class="card-3">
          The pitfalls of current social media is why the Coordinated
          Applicative Science Engine (CASE) was invented. With this application,
          resolution is the goal as well as meaningful dialogue. We provide a
          point system that heavily values the voice of the people, and train
          people to come to terms with differences in a way that creates change,
          not hardship. So come on and join us!<br>
        </p>
